(46979, 146656, 0, 1, 'Life', '我們重出生到現在是怎樣的人生路就一定要把它走完! 不能因為一些小小的挫折就被擊敗就想要逃避.........這樣是對自己的人生沒有一個態度跟交代.也不用去羨慕為什麼別人生下來就這麼好因為羨慕永遠羨慕不完.........\r\n', '2012-05-05 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'This our life we can not to elude \r\nLiving this life we must to thankyou\r\nAll the abundant life it`s coming from you\r\nMay the star(nature) and the sun thay`re still shiny\r\n\r\nMay the future we believe there still lovely\r\n\r\nAs we live  how many times we`ve been thinkin\r\nAs we die  how many thing we haven`t finished\r\nAs we try  how many thanks we should speaking\r\nAs we say  everything in this world we need to learning \r\n\r\nThis our life we can not to elude or escape \r\nLiving this life we must to thankyou\r\nAll the abundant life is coming from you\r\n\r\n\r\nMay the nature and the sun there still shiny\r\n\r\nMay the future we believe there still lovely \r\n\r\nMay the future we believe there still lovely\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', 217, '', 'Danny', 'Danny ', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-05 02:31:29', '2015-03-12 13:51:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
